text: Pontus Ek (born 27 June 1975) is a Swedish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Halmstad
